thread.title: Valued Customer

author: Valued Customer
title: Valued Customer
text: The website was superbly easy to navigate, and I was 95% sure I'd found the key I needed, but for ease of mind, I emailed a picture of the lock. Within ten minutes I'd received a response which verified the selection I'd thought was correct. I placed the order and it arrived in two business days, which I wouldn't have thought possible. It fit the lock and the problem was solved. Thanks, EasyKeys!
